00:17:56.270 --> 00:17:58.500 align:middle line:90%
and without trauma?

00:17:58.500 --> 00:18:01.730 align:middle line:84%
How do you wire the thought
you are not your grandma.

00:18:01.730 --> 00:18:03.170 align:middle line:90%
You are your own being.

00:18:03.170 --> 00:18:06.230 align:middle line:84%
You repeat this every day
to overwrite that program.

00:18:06.230 --> 00:18:09.830 align:middle line:84%
Are there other tools,
frequencies, music,

00:18:09.830 --> 00:18:12.410 align:middle line:84%
whatever that you can over--
dance that you can overwrite it

00:18:12.410 --> 00:18:13.660 align:middle line:90%
with while you're saying this?

00:18:13.660 --> 00:18:15.860 align:middle line:84%
>> SWART: Yeah, so using
any of your senses.

00:18:15.860 --> 00:18:18.200 align:middle line:84%
We all know about
the five senses.

00:18:18.200 --> 00:18:21.320 align:middle line:84%
But there are other senses too
like our temperature sensors,

00:18:21.320 --> 00:18:23.790 align:middle line:84%
thermoception, our pain
sensors, nociception.

00:18:23.790 --> 00:18:26.540 align:middle line:84%
And then my favorite
one is interoception,

00:18:26.540 --> 00:18:30.680 align:middle line:84%
which is your sense of the
state of the physiology

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:32.400 align:middle line:90%
of the inside of your body.

00:18:32.400 --> 00:18:34.460 align:middle line:84%
So, for example,
if you think about,

00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:37.640 align:middle line:84%
